parameters: Why did you call me here and then leave me alone
把我叫来之后就玩失踪对吧
Shio was here too, she always does that, when something interesting happens, it will get Frerlyn's full attention
汐也在啊，这家伙就是这样，碰到有趣的事情就什么都不管了
What's the matter with me? I haven't seen you today
又跟我有什么关系，我今天可没见过你哦
Stop, tell me, what do you want me to find out for you again?
别闹了，说吧，又想我帮你查什么？
I really haven't seen you today
Are you not telling the truth?
I should be trapped in... different space?
我应该是被困在了……异空间？
Yes, I've been trapped in a different space all day
对，被困在了异空间一整天了
You are really easy to encounter such strange things
你还真是容易碰到这种怪事啊
Of course, it may be that I lost my memory
当然也有可能是我失忆了
真的没有奇怪的地方吗？
I've been so obedient and busy with you all day. You don't even doubt it!?
我那么听话的陪你忙了一天你竟然一点都不怀疑的吗！？
不正常对你来说不才是正常吗？
Why is it abnormal to work hard
认真工作怎么就不正常了
也不是说没有奇怪的地方吧
Then you must have seen a ghost
So the one you saw must be fake
所以你见到的那个肯定是假冒的
Why people do that bored s**t?
真的会有人做那么无聊的事情吗……
Isn't the first thing you think about how she did it?
你第一时间想的竟然不是她是怎么做到的？
Welcome to the Supernatural Research Club
欢迎加入超自然研究部
I suddenly remembered the stage performence
If our story is a drama
如果我们的故事是一出剧目
"She" appeared in place of the actor
And lead the whole story to an unknown direction
将这个剧目的剧情，引导至一个未知的方向
No one knows where the story will go until the curtain closes
在落幕之前，没有人知道故事会变成怎样
It's a notebook I picked up yesterday, with The God Diary on the cover
是我昨天捡到的一本笔记本，封面写着神之日记
Can this The God Diary let me know what happened?
那这本《神之日记》能让我知道到底发生了什么吗？
So does it just write "March 3rd, Rain"?
上面是不是只写着"3月3日 下雨"？
I have read this God Diary, I guess
我好像，看过这本《神之日记》
At that time, I went into the men's washroom because the women's was under repair
那个时候，因为女厕所都正好在维修，所以我进了男厕所
然后出门碰见了王缪可……
对不上……记忆完全对不上……
I had the same day three times...for each day
每一天……我都经历了三次
And what I experiences was all different every time
A loop? Or to be more precise, a "reincarnation"?
循环？亦或者说是"轮回"更合适呢？
I wonder what did I do in the forst two reincarnations~
那前两次轮回里我都做了些什么呀~
That's what you cared about in the first place?
第一时间关心的竟然是这个吗？
Isn't something so interesting worth knowing in the first place!?That's a REINCARNATION!
这么有趣的事情难道不值得第一时间知道吗！？这可是轮回诶！
I saw your name in the first and second loops
前两次轮回里你的名字有出现过
So I'm the new character you met in THIS loop
所以说我是这次故事的新角色吗
What do you think about this experience
那你觉得这次的故事怎么样
Ridiculous? I have no proper adjective for it...
荒诞？我也不知道怎么形容了……
But it is interesting isn't it?
反正挺有意思的是不是~
Does "another me" presence make the story more interesting
另一个我的出现会不会也只是为了让故事更有趣呢
If the loop is not over, what kind of story would you like to see
如果轮回还会继续，你希望是什么故事呢
I don't know...If possible I rather like end it anyway
不知道……可以的话我更想结束轮回吧
But I don't want to forget these people I met during the loop...
但是又不太舍得的在这些重复的时间里认识的人……
No worries, just met them from the beginning
这有什么好烦恼的，重新去认识不就行了
You already did it once, just repeat it
反正都认识过一次了，再来一次又不难是吧
西卡同学~怎么一直不说话呢~
No, I just feel like...it's not something I can be a part of...
你们这话题……我好像真插不上话……
What can I say, as expected of your club
怎么说呢，不愧是超自然研究部呢
By the way, where is The God Diary now
对了，那《神之日记》现在在哪
It's in the activity room. If you want to see it, go and get it now
就放在活动室那，你想看的话现在去拿好了
Freelyn leads me and Ceka to the door of room
菲林拉着我和西卡回到了活动室门前
我突然间想起了一件事
Freelyn glanced at me for a second
But Ceka already opened the room door
而西卡拉开了活动室的门
我被黑色的虚无包裹着
Before I lost consciousness, a WangMilk's face went through my mind
在意识又一次涣散之前，我的脑海中闪过的，是王缪可的脸
